		<div id="comment_body_64570579"><p>Sure, but now I have to take a photo of every price tag as I shop. I'm going to take that into account, so I will be less willing to buy large numbers of items. Stores like Walmart depend on impulse buys from foot traffic. But now that impulse is going to fight with laziness, and I think Walmart will lose.</p></div>
	</div>

